<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><!DOCTYPE paragraph PUBLIC "-//IFRS//DTD DITA Paragraph//EN" "../../../DocTypes/com.ifrs.doctype/dtd/paragraph.dtd"><paragraph id="IAS34_54"><paranum class="- topic/title paragraph/paranum "/><titlealts><navtitle>54</navtitle></titlealts><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IAS&#xa0;34"/><data name="paranum" value="54"/></prolog><body><variant base="F21341302" id="IAS34_54_V1"> <p id="IAS34_P0231"><ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Investment Entities</ph></ph> (Amendments to <xref base="F24730975" href="../ifrs10/IFRS10_TOC.dita#IFRS10_TOC0001" id="IAS34_X0256">IFRS&#xa0;10</xref>, <xref base="F24730976" href="../ifrs12/IFRS12_TOC.dita#IFRS12_TOC0001" id="IAS34_X0257">IFRS&#xa0;12</xref> and <xref base="F24730977" href="../ias27/IAS27_TOC0001.dita#IAS27_TOC0001" id="IAS34_X0258">IAS&#xa0;27</xref>), issued in October 2012, amended <xref base="F26333917" href="IAS34_16A.dita#IAS34_16A" id="IAS34_X0259">paragraph 16A</xref>. An entity shall apply that amendment for annual periods beginning on or after 1 January 2014. Earlier application of <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Investment Entities</ph></ph> is permitted. If an entity applies that amendment earlier it shall also apply all amendments included in <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Investment Entities</ph></ph> at the same time.</p></variant></body></paragraph>